# WebAuthn / passkeys. WEBAUTHN_RP_ID is the apex domain (no scheme, no port);
# use "localhost" for local dev. WEBAUTHN_EXPECTED_ORIGIN is a comma-separated
# list of allowed front-end origins (scheme + host + optional port). Every
# origin that can register or sign in must appear here.
